<text><body>
<lb n="0464b17" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0464b18" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0464b19" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 1313</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0464b20" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0464001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note>佛說救拔熖口餓鬼陀羅尼經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0464b21" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0464b22" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0464002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…門））四十一字＝（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十一字【宋】【元】，（（唐三藏沙門大廣智））八字【明】【甲】</note><note n="0464002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…門）四十一字【大】，大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智【宋】【元】，唐三藏沙門大廣智【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464002" cb:word-count="41"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0464b23" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空謚大鑒
<lb n="0464b24" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">唐三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0464b25" ed="T"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0464b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0464b2601">爾時，世尊在迦毘羅城尼<note n="0464003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俱＝拘【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俱【大】，拘【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464003"><lem wit="【大】">俱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">拘</rdg></app>律那僧伽藍所，
<lb n="0464b27" ed="T"/>與諸比丘，并諸菩薩，無數眾會，前後圍遶，而
<lb n="0464b28" ed="T"/>為說法。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0464b2804" cb:place="inline">爾時，阿難獨居靜處，念所受法。即於
<lb n="0464b29" ed="T"/>其夜三更已後，見一餓鬼，名曰「焰口」，其形醜
<pb n="0464c" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1313.0464c"/>
<lb n="0464c01" ed="T"/>陋、身體枯瘦、口中火然、咽如針鋒、頭髮<note n="0464004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓬＝髼【三】＊</note><note n="0464004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蓬【大】＊，髼【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0464004"><lem wit="【大】">蓬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">髼</rdg></app>亂、
<lb n="0464c02" ed="T"/>爪牙長利，甚可怖畏，住阿難前，白阿難言：「却
<lb n="0464c03" ed="T"/>後三日，汝命將盡，即便生<note n="0464005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝此【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，此【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464005"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">此</rdg></app>餓鬼之中。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0464c0316" cb:place="inline">是時，
<lb n="0464c04" ed="T"/>阿難聞此語已，心生惶怖，問餓鬼言：「若我死
<lb n="0464c05" ed="T"/>後，生餓鬼者，行何方便，得免斯苦？」</p>
<lb n="0464c06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0464c0601">爾時，餓鬼白阿難<note n="0464006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝曰【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，曰【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464006"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">曰</rdg></app>：「汝於明日，若能布施百
<lb n="0464c07" ed="T"/>千那由他恒河沙數餓鬼，并百千婆羅門仙
<lb n="0464c08" ed="T"/>等，以摩伽陀國所用之斛，各施一斛飲食，并
<lb n="0464c09" ed="T"/>及為我供養三寶，汝得增壽，令我離於餓鬼
<lb n="0464c10" ed="T"/>之苦、得生天上。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0464c1007" cb:place="inline">阿難見此焰口餓鬼，身形羸
<lb n="0464c11" ed="T"/>瘦、枯燋極醜、口中火然、咽如針鋒、頭髮<app type="star" corresp="#0464004"><lem wit="【大】">蓬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">髼</rdg></app>亂、
<lb n="0464c12" ed="T"/><note n="0464007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毛爪＝爪牙【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">毛爪【大】，爪牙【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464007"><lem wit="【大】">毛爪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">爪牙</rdg></app>長利，又聞如是不順之語，甚大驚怖，身
<lb n="0464c13" ed="T"/>毛皆竪。即從座起，疾至佛所，五體投地，頂禮
<lb n="0464c14" ed="T"/>佛足，身體<note n="0464008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戰＝顫【三】</note><note n="0464008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">戰【大】，顫【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0464008"><lem wit="【大】">戰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">顫</rdg></app>慄，而白佛言：「願救我苦！所以者
<lb n="0464c15" ed="T"/>何？我住靜處，念所<note n="0464009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">授＝受【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">授【大】，受【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464009"><lem wit="【大】">授</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">受</rdg></app>法，見焰口餓鬼，而語我
<lb n="0464c16" ed="T"/>言：『汝過三日，必當命盡，生餓鬼中。』我即問言：
<lb n="0464c17" ed="T"/>『云何令我得免斯苦？』餓鬼答言：『汝今若能施
<lb n="0464c18" ed="T"/>於百千那由他恒河沙數餓鬼，及百千婆羅
<lb n="0464c19" ed="T"/>門仙等種種飲食，汝得增壽。』世尊！我今云何
<lb n="0464c20" ed="T"/>能辦若干餓鬼、仙人等食？」</p>
<lb n="0464c21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0464c2101">爾時，世尊告阿難言：「汝今勿怖！我有方便，令
<lb n="0464c22" ed="T"/>汝能施若干百千恒河沙餓鬼，及諸婆羅門
<lb n="0464c23" ed="T"/>仙等，種種飲食，勿生憂惱。」</p>
<lb n="0464c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0464c2401">佛告阿難：「有陀羅尼，名曰『無量威德自在光
<lb n="0464c25" ed="T"/>明<note n="0464010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔殊〕－【甲】</note><note n="0464010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殊【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0464010"><lem wit="【大】">殊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>勝妙力』。若有誦此陀羅尼者，即能充足
<lb n="0464c26" ed="T"/>俱胝那由他百千恒河沙數餓鬼，及婆羅門
<lb n="0464c27" ed="T"/>仙等，上妙飲食。如是等眾，乃至一一，皆得摩
<lb n="0464c28" ed="T"/>伽陀國所用之斛七七斛食。阿難！我於前世
<lb n="0464c29" ed="T"/>作婆羅門，於觀<note n="0464011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世音＝自在【三】【甲】</note><note n="0464011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世音【大】，自在【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0464011"><lem wit="【大】">世音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">自在</rdg></app>菩薩所，及世間自在威
<pb n="0465a" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1313.0465a"/>
<lb n="0465a01" ed="T"/>德如來所，受此陀羅尼故，能散施與無量餓
<lb n="0465a02" ed="T"/>鬼及諸仙等種種飲食，令諸餓鬼解脫苦身、
<lb n="0465a03" ed="T"/>得生天上。阿難！汝今受持，福德、壽命皆得增
<lb n="0465a04" ed="T"/>長。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0465a0402" cb:place="inline">爾時，世尊即為阿難說陀羅尼曰：</p>
<lb n="0465a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a0501" cb:type="dharani">「<note n="0465001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那謨＝曩莫【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那謨【大】，曩莫【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465001"><lem wit="【大】">那謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">曩莫</rdg></app>　薩<note n="0465002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩＋（無可反下同）【元】，（無可切下同）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，嚩無可反下同【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->嚩無可切下同【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465002"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">嚩無可反下同</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">嚩無可切下同</rdg></app>　怛<note n="0465003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（引）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他【大】，他(引)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465003"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">他<note place="inline">引</note></rdg></app><note n="0465004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蘖多引＝蘖跢引一【宋】【元】，<g ref="#CB00858"/>跢引一【明】</note><note n="0465004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蘖多引【大】，蘖跢引一【宋】【元】，<g ref="#CB00858"/>跢引一【明】</note><app n="0465004"><lem wit="【大】">蘖多<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">蘖跢引一</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><g ref="#CB00858"/>跢引一</rdg></app>　嚩<note n="0465005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盧＝路引【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盧【大】，路引【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465005"><lem wit="【大】">盧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">路引</rdg></app>枳<note n="0465006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（二）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝【大】，帝(二)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465006"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝<note place="inline">二</note></rdg></app>　<note n="0465007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唵參婆囉參婆囉吽＝唵引三三去跋羅三拔羅吽引四【宋】【元】，唵引三三去聲跋羅三跋羅吽引四【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唵參婆囉參婆囉吽【大】，唵引三三去跋羅三拔羅吽引四【宋】【元】，唵引三三去聲跋羅三跋羅吽引四【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465007"><lem wit="【大】">唵
<lb n="0465a06" ed="T"/>　參婆囉　參婆囉　吽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">唵引三三去跋羅三拔羅吽引四</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">唵引三三去聲跋羅三跋羅吽引四</rdg></app>」</p>
<lb n="0465a07" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a0701">佛告阿難：「若有善男子、善女人，欲求長壽、福
<lb n="0465a08" ed="T"/>德增榮，速能滿足檀波羅蜜，每於晨朝、及一
<lb n="0465a09" ed="T"/>切時，悉無障礙，取一淨器，盛以淨水，置少<note n="0465008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＝飲【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯【大】，飲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465008"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">飲</rdg></app>
<lb n="0465a10" ed="T"/><g ref="#CB00595"/>及諸餅<note n="0465009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＝飯【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，飯【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465009"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">飯</rdg></app>等，以右手<note n="0465010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">加＝按【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">加【大】，按【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465010"><lem wit="【大】">加</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">按</rdg></app>器，誦前陀羅尼
<lb n="0465a11" ed="T"/>滿七遍，然後稱四如來名號：</p>
<lb n="0465a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a1201" cb:type="dharani">「<note n="0465011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南謨多寶如來）＋曩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】，南謨多寶如來曩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465011"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">南謨多寶如來曩</rdg></app>謨　<note n="0465012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＋（去）夾註【宋】【元】，（去聲）【明】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆【大】＊，婆(去)【宋】【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->婆去聲【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465012"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">婆<note place="inline">去</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">婆去聲</rdg></app>誐嚩<note n="0465013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（一）夾註【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝【大】，帝(一)【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465013"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝<note place="inline">一</note></rdg></app>　鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0465014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔枳孃二合〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枳孃二合【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465014"><lem wit="【大】">枳孃<note place="inline">二合</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>部<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0465a13" ed="T"/><note n="0465015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＝哆【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】，哆【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465015"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">哆</rdg></app>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>　<note n="0465016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（野）＋怛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怛【大】，野怛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465016"><lem wit="【大】">怛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">野怛</rdg></app><note n="0465017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（引）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465017" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->他【大】＊，他引【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465017"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">他引</rdg></app>孽<note n="0465018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多也此云多寶如來＝跢引野二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多也此云多寶如來【大】，跢引野二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465018"><lem wit="【大】">多也<note place="inline">此云多寶如來</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">跢引野二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a1401">「由稱多寶如來名號加持故，能破一切諸鬼
<lb n="0465a15" ed="T"/>多生已來慳悋惡<note n="0465019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">業＋（罪障消滅）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">業【大】，業罪障消滅【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465019"><lem wit="【大】">業</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">業罪障消滅</rdg></app>，即得福德圓滿。</p>
<lb n="0465a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a1601" cb:type="dharani">「<note n="0465020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">那＝南謨妙色身如來曩【三】，曩【甲】</note><note n="0465020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">那【大】，南謨妙色身如來曩【宋】【元】【明】，曩【甲】</note><app n="0465020"><lem wit="【大】">那</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">南謨妙色身如來曩</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">曩</rdg></app>謨　婆誐<note n="0465021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩＝縛【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，縛【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465021"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">縛</rdg></app><note n="0465022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帝＋（一）【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">帝【大】＊，帝一【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465022"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝一</rdg></app>　素嚕<note n="0465023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波引耶＝二合播引野【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">波引耶【大】，二合播引野【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465023"><lem wit="【大】">波<note place="inline">引</note>耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">二合播引野</rdg></app>　怛他誐<note n="0465024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哆＝跢【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">哆【大】，跢【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465024"><lem wit="【大】">哆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">跢</rdg></app>
<lb n="0465a17" ed="T"/>野<note place="inline"><note n="0465025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此云南無妙色身如來＝二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此云南無妙色身如來【大】，二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465025"><lem wit="【大】">此云南無妙色身如來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">二</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0465a18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a1801">「由稱妙色身如來名號加持故，能破諸鬼醜
<lb n="0465a19" ed="T"/>陋惡形，即得色相具足。</p>
<lb n="0465a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a2001" cb:type="dharani">「<note n="0465026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南謨廣博身如來）＋曩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】，南謨廣博身如來曩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465026"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">南謨廣博身如來曩</rdg></app><note n="0465027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＋（引）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">謨【大】，謨引【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465027"><lem wit="【大】">謨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">謨引</rdg></app>　婆誐嚩<app type="star" corresp="#0465022"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝一</rdg></app>　尾<note n="0465028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（鉢囉…來））二十五字＝（（補羅誐引怛囉二合引野怛他引孽跢引野二））十八字【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（鉢囉…來）二十五字【大】，補羅誐引怛囉二合引野怛他引孽跢引野二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465028" cb:word-count="25"><lem wit="【大】">鉢囉<note place="inline">二合</note>誐攞孽多怛
<lb n="0465a21" ed="T"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note>也　怛他孽多也<note place="inline">此云廣博身如來</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">補羅誐引怛囉二合引野怛他引孽跢引野二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a2201">「由稱廣博身如來名號加持故，能令諸鬼咽
<lb n="0465a23" ed="T"/>喉寬大，所施之食，恣意充飽。</p>
<lb n="0465a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a2401" cb:type="dharani">「<note n="0465029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（南謨離怖如來）＋曩【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">曩【大】，南謨離怖如來曩【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465029"><lem wit="【大】">曩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">南謨離怖如來曩</rdg></app>謨　<app type="star" corresp="#0465012"><lem wit="【大】">婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">婆去聲</rdg></app>誐嚩<app type="star" corresp="#0465022"><lem wit="【大】">帝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">帝一</rdg></app>　阿<note place="inline"><note n="0465030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，上聲【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465030"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">上聲</rdg></app></note>婆<note place="inline"><note n="0465031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">去＋（聲）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，去聲【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465031"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">去聲</rdg></app></note>孕迦<note n="0465032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">囉也＝囉引野【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">囉也【大】，囉引野【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465032"><lem wit="【大】">囉也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">囉引野</rdg></app>　怛
<lb n="0465a25" ed="T"/><note n="0465033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（去）【宋】【元】，（去聲）【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他【大】，他去【宋】【元】，<!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->他去聲【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465033"><lem wit="【大】">他</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">他去</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【甲】">他去聲</rdg></app>蘖<note n="0465034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多也此云離怖畏如來＝哆引野二【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多也此云離怖畏如來【大】，哆引野二【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465034"><lem wit="【大】">多也<note place="inline">此云離怖畏如來</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">哆引野二</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0465a26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465a2601">「由稱離怖畏如來名號加持故，能令諸鬼一
<lb n="0465a27" ed="T"/>切恐怖悉皆除滅，離餓鬼趣。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0465a2712" cb:place="inline">佛告阿難：「若族
<lb n="0465a28" ed="T"/>姓<note n="0465035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善男子等既＝子等【三】，子等既【甲】</note><note n="0465035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善男子等既【大】，子等【宋】【元】【明】，子等既【甲】</note><app n="0465035"><lem wit="【大】">善男子等，既</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">子等</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">子等既</rdg></app>稱四如來名號加持已，彈指
<lb n="0465a29" ed="T"/>七遍，取於食器，於淨地上，展臂瀉之。作此施
<pb n="0465b" ed="T" xml:id="T21.1313.0465b"/>
<lb n="0465b01" ed="T"/>已，於其四方，有百千那由他恒河沙數餓鬼，
<lb n="0465b02" ed="T"/>前<note n="0465036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（各）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各【大】，各各【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465036"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">各各</rdg></app>有摩伽陀國七七斛食。受此食已，悉皆
<lb n="0465b03" ed="T"/>飽滿，是諸<note n="0465037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鬼等悉＝餓鬼悉等【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鬼等悉【大】，餓鬼悉等【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465037"><lem wit="【大】">鬼等，悉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">餓鬼悉等</rdg></app>捨鬼身，生於天上。</p>
<lb n="0465b04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0465b0401">「阿難！若有比丘、比丘尼、優婆塞、優婆夷，常以
<lb n="0465b05" ed="T"/>此<note n="0465038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">密＝真【三】【甲】＊</note><note n="0465038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">密【大】＊，真【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0465038"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">真</rdg></app>言及四如來名號加持食<note n="0465039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施＋（餓）【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施【大】，施餓【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465039"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">施餓</rdg></app>鬼，便能
<lb n="0465b06" ed="T"/>具足無量福德，則同供養百千俱胝如來功
<lb n="0465b07" ed="T"/>德等無差別，壽命延長、增益色力、善根具足，
<lb n="0465b08" ed="T"/>一切非人、夜叉、羅剎、諸惡鬼神不敢侵害，又
<lb n="0465b09" ed="T"/>能成就無量福德壽命。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0465b0910" cb:place="inline">「若欲施諸婆羅門仙
<lb n="0465b10" ed="T"/>等，以淨飲食滿盛一器，即以前<app type="star" corresp="#0465038"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">真</rdg></app>言加持二
<lb n="0465b11" ed="T"/>七遍，投於淨流水中。如是作已，即為以天
<lb n="0465b12" ed="T"/><note n="0465040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仙＝諸【元】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0465040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">仙【大】，諸【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465040"><lem wit="【大】">仙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【甲】">諸</rdg></app>美妙<note n="0465041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝飲【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，飲【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465041"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">飲</rdg></app>食，供養百千俱胝恒河沙數婆
<lb n="0465b13" ed="T"/>羅門仙。彼諸仙人得加持食故，<note n="0465042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以密言＝以呪【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以密言【大】，以呪【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465042"><lem wit="【大】">以密言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">以呪</rdg></app>威德，
<lb n="0465b14" ed="T"/>各各成就根本所願、諸善功德，各各同時發
<lb n="0465b15" ed="T"/>誓願言：『願<note n="0465043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝施【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，施【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465043"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">施</rdg></app>食人，<note n="0465044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">令壽＝壽命【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">令壽【大】，壽命【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465044"><lem wit="【大】">令壽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">壽命</rdg></app>延長、色力安樂；又
<lb n="0465b16" ed="T"/>令其人，心所見聞，正解清淨，具足成就梵天
<lb n="0465b17" ed="T"/>威德、行梵天行。又同供養百千恒河沙如來
<lb n="0465b18" ed="T"/>功德，一切冤讎不能侵害。』</p><p xml:id="pT21p0465b1811" cb:place="inline">「若比丘、比丘尼、優
<lb n="0465b19" ed="T"/>婆塞、優婆夷，若欲供養佛、法、僧寶，應以香、華
<lb n="0465b20" ed="T"/>及淨飲食，以前<app type="star" corresp="#0465038"><lem wit="【大】">密</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">真</rdg></app>言加持二十一遍，奉獻三
<lb n="0465b21" ed="T"/>寶。是善男子、<note n="0465045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（及）＋善【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，及善【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465045"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">及善</rdg></app>女人，則成以天餚饍上味，
<lb n="0465b22" ed="T"/>奉獻供養滿十方<note n="0465046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（世）＋界【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">界【大】，世界【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465046"><lem wit="【大】">界</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">世界</rdg></app>佛、法、僧寶，亦為讚歎、勸
<lb n="0465b23" ed="T"/>請、隨喜功德，恒為諸佛憶念稱讚，諸天善神
<lb n="0465b24" ed="T"/>恒來擁護，即為滿足檀波羅蜜。</p><p xml:id="pT21p0465b2413" cb:place="inline">「阿難！汝隨我
<lb n="0465b25" ed="T"/>語，如法修行，廣宣流布，令諸眾生普得見聞，
<lb n="0465b26" ed="T"/>獲無量福。是名『救焰口餓鬼及苦眾生陀羅
<lb n="0465b27" ed="T"/>尼經』，以是名字，汝當奉持。」</p><p xml:id="pT21p0465b2711" cb:place="inline">一切大眾及阿難
<lb n="0465b28" ed="T"/>等，聞佛說已，一心信受，歡喜奉行。</p>
<lb n="0465b29" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0465047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛說）＋救【三】【甲】</note><note n="0465047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">救【大】，佛說救【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0465047"><lem wit="【大】">救</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">佛說救</rdg></app><note n="0465048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔拔〕－【宋】【元】</note><note n="0465048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拔【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】</note><app n="0465048"><lem wit="【大】">拔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>焰口餓鬼陀羅尼經<note n="0465049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本有貞享四年中春十九夕一校點之淨嚴四十九歲元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</note><note n="0465049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔－〕【大】，貞享四年中春十九夕一校點之淨嚴四十九歲元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教【甲】</note><app n="0465049"><lem wit="【大】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">貞享四年中春十九夕一校點之淨嚴四十九歲元祿十六年二月十六日以淨嚴和上之本再校了尊教</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>